msgstr "espeak(1), उत्सव(1), mbrola(1), freetts(1)"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmouth.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/kmouth"
"\">help:/kmouth</ulink> (either enter this &URL; into &konqueror;, or run "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kmouth</"
"parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"अधिकविस्तृतं उपयोक्तृदस्तावेजं <ulink url=\"help:/kmouth\">help:/kmouth</ulink> "
"इत्यस्मात् उपलभ्यते (एतत् &URL; &konqueror; मध्ये प्रविशतु, अथवा "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> < चालयन्तु पैरामीटर>सहायता:/kmouth</"
"parameter></userinput>)।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmouth.1.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also further information available at the <ulink url=\"https://"
